Deemos and his gang, now named the Chosen Ones, tried to call out Psuedo in=
 front of the Predacon base, but no show. (Predacon base, NOT cave) Psuedo =
wanted to come out, but Blackarachnia ordered him to stand guard inside of =
the base.

"That's it, if Psuedo won't come out, so we destroy the base, ei=
ther way, he shall die!" Deemos said.

"Destroy the base?" Artist asked.

"=
It's okay, because it will be for a good cause." Deemos said. Artist smiled=
, he should never have doubted Deemos!

Diskus flew in and fired 2 missiles=
 at The Predacon base. Artist posed and fired 4 electrical blasts at the Pr=
edacon base. Doom Ice threw a grenade at the Predacon base. Stronghold fire=
s 4 optic blasts at the Predacon base. Blender fires a rocket at the Predac=
on base. Airbomber fires 25 machine gun shots at the Predacon base. Rizopas=
 fires 4 shots at the Predacon base. Deemos sits back and smiles while rubb=
ing his hands together...
